    "faq1Question": "Oomisha akkamittan maxxansa?",
    "faq1Answer": "Tabii Oomishaalee ykn cuqaasaa Maxxansi jedhu daashboordii kee irraa tuqi. Gosa oomishaa, baay'ina, gatii, fi iddoo guuti. Beeksisni kee battaluma sanatti ifa ta'a.",
